reviewText: It only has 3 songs.  I was overcharged because I wanted a concert and I got 3 live songs and I paid as much as I would have paid for a CD.  I was very disappointed.  It was actually a promotional DVD - it was not what was advertised i.e. a concert DVD with Tim McGraw performing.
It did not meet my expectations. I returned.
You can't go wrong with Tim McGraw.  Not only is his music super;  he's wonderful to look at.
